disarmament 
the pershing missiles were the delivery systems for 
europeanbased nuclear warheads aimed at the soviet union under 
terms of the intermediaterange nuclear forces treaty that took 
effect june 1 the united states has two years to destroy 450 
missiles in turn the soviet union will destroy a larger number of 
