2 1986 there was a bomb scare when the bolshoi ballet opened at 
lincoln center in july 1987 a car at the soviet residential complex 
in the bronx was firebombed in 1984 
five protest groups have obtained permits to demonstrate outside 
the united nations during gorbachevs appearance before the general 
assembly including the coalition for soviet jewry the students for 
soviet jewry and organizations representing afghans ukrainians and 
armenians 
police spokesman sgt peter sweeney said this is going to be a 
major major operation by the new york city police department in 
both manpower and traffic problems 
police chief robert johnston jr said 6600 officers will be 
assigned to work overtime on the visit at a cost of more than 1 
million we are going to document every cops assignment and apply 
for reimbursement to the state department he said 
the police will coordinate the security effort with the secret 
service the state department and the united nations 250member 
police force 
when asked to characterize the force that will be in place 
anthony oconnell the united nations security chief said the 
standards of security that are normal at this headquarters for the 
visits of heads of state 
when about 90 heads of government attended the united nations 
40th anniversary hundreds of city police as well as teams of 
police scuba divers helicopter patrols and mounted officers watched 
the events conscious of possible terrorist attacks 
the police harbor unit stationed patrol boats off the un 
complex on the east river around the clock teams of police divers 
performed daily searches of the riverfront piers for bombs 
in 1981 when prince charles of britain paid a oneday visit to 
new york city and lunched with president and mrs reagan he was 
guarded by a 2000member security force which included 1725 city 
police officers 
the biggest and most costly security and crowd and traffic 
control operation was the october 1979 visit of pope john paul ii 
the twoday papal visit involved more than 13000 city police 
officers and cost more than 3 million 
